  "title": "水蛭（Leech）[Anki, SuperMemo]",
  "image_width": 2160,
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"PlPh1L_D\"><b>Leeches </b>in <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/SuperMemo\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo</a> are questions that a student keeps <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Forgetting\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">forgetting</a>. Most often leeches come from disrespect for the <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/20_rules_of_knowledge_formulation\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">20 rules of knowledge formulation</a>. Some well-formulated material may also need a boost from mnemonic techniques or a boost in <a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//supermemo.guru/wiki/Coherence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">coherence</a>, e.g. by setting questions in relevant context.</p><p data-pid=\"N7O7VWTF\">SuperMemo 中的 Leech 指的是学生经常遗忘的问题。大多数情况下，Leech 来自对知识表述的 20 条规则<sup data-text=\"20 条知识表述规则\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/269997143\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>的不尊重。一些表述良好的材料可能还需要加强助记技巧或增强连贯性<sup data-text=\"一致性与连贯性\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/264327134\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"2\">[2]</sup>，例如在相关的上下文设置问题。</p>",
